{"word":"G1287 - διασκορπίζω - diaskorpízō - dee-as-kor-pid'-zo - Disperse","slug":"G1287","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">διασκορπίζω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>diaskorpízō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>dee-as-kor-pid'-zo"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Disperse"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03B4;&#x03B9;&#x03B1;&#x03C3;&#x03BA;&#x03BF;&#x03C1;&#x03C0;&#x03B9;&#x0301;&#x03B6;&#x03C9; - diaskorpizo&#x0304;</b> - <i>dee-as-kor-pid'-zo</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G1223\">G1223</a> and <a href=\"#/G4650\">G4650</a>; to <i>dissipate</i>, that is, (generally) to <i>rout</i> or <i>separate</i>; specifically to <i>winnow</i>; figuratively to <i>squander:</i> - disperse, scatter (abroad), strew, waste."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G4650\">G4650</a>"}]}